## Implementation Roadmap

| Phase | Timeline | Key Tasks | Responsible Party | Deliverables | Success Criteria |
|-------|----------|-----------|-------------------|--------------|------------------|
| **Preparation Phase** | M1 | Pause mechanism design, security organization partnership agreements, technical specification review | Core Team + Security Team | Finalized pause mechanism design, partnership agreements | Technical review approval >90% |
| **Development Phase** | M1-M2 | Smart contract pause functionality implementation, comprehensive testing | Development Team | Pause-enabled contracts, test suite | 100% test coverage, security audit passed |
| **Security Phase** | M2-M3 | Professional security audit, vulnerability assessment | External Auditors | Security audit report, remediation | Zero critical/high vulnerabilities |
| **Testing Phase** | M2-M3 | Testnet deployment, pause mechanism simulation, community testing | QA Team + Community | Testnet deployment, test results | Zero critical bugs, community feedback integration |
| **Deployment Phase** | M3-M4 | Mainnet deployment, documentation, community education | Operations Team | Live pause mechanism, comprehensive docs | Successful deployment, community understanding >80% |

