## Community Impact Assessment

| Stakeholders | Impact Analysis | Impact Level | Mitigation Measures | Responsible Party |
|--------------|-----------------|--------------|---------------------|-------------------|
| **Contract Users** | Enhanced asset protection during attacks, reduced risk of irreversible losses | Highly Positive | Clear communication, transparent pause procedures | Security Team |
| **Security Organizations** | Authorized pause capabilities, increased responsibility | Positive | Partnership agreements, clear guidelines | Technical Committee |
| **Community Members** | Ability to initiate emergency pauses through governance | Positive | Proposal templates, educational materials | Community Manager |
| **Developers** | Additional pause functionality to implement and maintain | Medium | Technical documentation, development support | Development Team |
